Titolo: Disciples: Sacred Lands

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: Disciples: Sacred Lands is a turn-based PC strategy game published by Strategy First in 1999. Set in a fantasy world known as the Sacred Lands, it depicts a battle for dominance between four races of the world of Nevendaar: The Empire (humans), the Mountain Clans (dwarves) the Legions of the Damned (demons), and the Undead Hordes (undead). In 2001, an expanded version of the game was released titled Disciples: Sacred Lands - Gold Edition. It added 25 new scenarios.